PN,41301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773843068
OL,3,CAuthor Michael Rosen urges people to
OL,4,C'look everywhere' for meningitis rash
OL,6,FAuthor Michael Rosen, whose son Eddie
OL,7,Fdied from meningitis in 1999, has
OL,8,Fwarned people to "look everywhere" for
OL,9,Fthe rash associated with the infection.
OL,11,FThe 79-year-old, who is best known for
OL,12,Fthe children's book We're Going On A
OL,13,FBear Hunt, was speaking following an
OL,14,Foutbreak of the infection in Kent,
OL,15,Fwhich has recently seen the total
OL,16,Fnumber of cases being investigated by
OL,17,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,18,Frise to 20.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
